text: Hong Chul-ho (born 2 June 1968) is a South Korean rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of South Korea Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
